@startuml
participant "API Server" as API
participant "Router Engine" as Router
participant "Experiment Engine" as Experiment
participant "Ensembler" as Ensembler
participant "Batch Ensembler Engine" as BatchEnsembler
participant "Logging Service" as Logging
participant "Monitoring Service" as Monitoring
participant "Kubernetes" as K8s

API -> Router: Create/Update Router
Router -> K8s: Deploy Router
API -> Experiment: Configure Experiment
API -> Ensembler: Configure Ensembler
API -> BatchEnsembler: Submit Batch Job
BatchEnsembler -> K8s: Deploy Spark Job

Router -> Experiment: Get Experiment Configuration
Router -> Ensembler: Route Traffic
Ensembler -> Router: Return Combined Results

Router -> Logging: Log Results
Router -> Monitoring: Send Metrics

API -> K8s: Retrieve Pod Logs
K8s --> API: Return Pod Logs

API -> Monitoring: Configure Alerting Rules
Monitoring -> K8s: Apply Alerting Configuration

@enduml